Not just a pretty little piece of furniture


Our Coffee & Side Tables are great pieces of furniture to add to your living room, bringing both form and function to the fore. Our stylish ARKELSTORP coffee table with cleverly designed drop leaves is both practical and drop dead gorgeous. Think less is more? The TOFTERYD table in high gloss white is perfect for minimalistic homes. Our HAVSTA collections nest of tables come in sets of two. Use each table individually or slide one under the other when you need the extra space.
